cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CR 

This paper is about person re-identification, which is a computer vision task. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, such as kernel functions and density estimation, which could fall under cs.MM (Machine Learning) and cs.LG (Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses ranking and similarity measures, which could be relevant to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
